data.description:
Home is located on over a half-acre lot at the end of a dirt road, offering a peaceful and quiet atmosphere. Recently renovated in 2021, the home has modern updates including new LVP flooring, upgraded countertops, and a beautifully tiled shower. The open floorplan of this home creates a spacious and inviting environment. With three bedrooms and two full bathrooms, there is plenty of room for comfortable living. Additionally, this home includes two storage sheds, providing ample space for outdoor storage.

The home is also equipped with water filtration systems under the sinks, ensuring clean and pure water for everyday use. This feature adds convenience and peace of mind for the homeowners. Whether you're looking for a peaceful getaway or a quiet place to call home, this property offers the perfect blend of tranquility and modern comfort.
